            <h2>🥳 Fun Facts About Crisps! 🥳</h2>
            <img src="lays_realistic.jpg" alt="A bag of Lay's chips">
            <ul>
                <li>🥔 The very first potato chip was made in 1853 by George Crum.</li>
                <li>🌍 Lay’s chips are sold under different names worldwide, like Walkers in the UK and Sabritas in Mexico.</li>
                <li>📦 The biggest bag of chips ever made weighed over 2,500 pounds!</li>
                <li>🧂 The first-ever flavored crisps were **cheese & onion**, introduced in the 1950s.</li>
                <li>🍠 Pringles are **not technically potato chips** – they’re made from dehydrated potato flakes.</li>
            </ul>

